name: Nobara - Jujutsu kaisen
description:
I made this because i was pretty unhappy with all the nobara's around that...didn't look like the character.

Like Android 18, i like it close to the original stuff so a little style baked in is nice.

Trained 80 ish images from the anime, trained on NAI (please dont train loras on mixes), Pictures are from AOM3.

For the uniform: school uniform,jacket,gakuran

If you like it, good for you :)
If you don't, well...there are other options around.
Also if you like it give me money. money good. I'm kidding, did this in a few minutes anyway, buy yourself a sandwich or something.

Please rename the file. Some images are from a previous epoch but they were nice enough so I included them here.
